{"tid":1268228,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"證《寒戰》李Sir最紅　梁家輝：仲有唔少人嗌我九叔！","createTime":"2019-06-30T08:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T09:05:57.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eb72cdb6a50d56973566cfb9e7a23d3b1ee1370a","tid":1268228,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2891132/org/b9d2f30aa54903192528d31b2c673496.jpg/ciZ-kS84lNx6UfCYPpPX5AKTcJdegmQY9rhFYNy4RWA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2891132%2Forg%2Fb9d2f30aa54903192528d31b2c673496.jpg%2FciZ-kS84lNx6UfCYPpPX5AKTcJdegmQY9rhFYNy4RWA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2196e239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁家輝的演技一早備受肯定，他曾四奪香港電影金像獎最佳男主角，最早一次更是憑1984年《垂簾聽政》飾演咸豐帝奪得，其餘三次分別是《92黑玫瑰對黑玫瑰》奇哥（1993）、《黑社會》大D哥（2006），以及《寒戰》李Sir（2013）。<br />\n<br />\n如何才算是一位成功演員，除了獎項，另一指標是走到街上，途人能否叫得出自己演過的角色名。有時被途人叫得出角色名，比記起自己真名會更高興，這證明自己的演出深人民心，是一份肯定。問到梁家輝近年最多人在街上叫他甚麼？「李Sir（《寒戰》李文彬），<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我有時將架車泊在金鐘警察總部附近，行經時會有警員向我打招呼叫我李Sir，甚至有些會向我敬禮，又打趣說︰『點呀一哥，返嚟坐下呀？』相當有趣。</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n至於在網上大受歡迎的九叔（《大丈夫》角色），原來都是途人的選擇之一，不過就有特定的年齡界線。梁家輝笑說︰「都有唔少人嗌我九叔，不過多數是一些年過四十，相信已經很久未入戲院睇戲的朋友。」這是家輝哥的個人分析，相信是基於電影屬2003年的作品，大家仍在懷緬這個角色罷了。<br />\n<br />\n其實九叔之所以咁受歡迎，可能對於一班男士來說，都想身邊有一個這樣有情有義的兄弟。大家一齊出嚟玩，被太太們掃場，自己中招後沒有同兄弟攬炒，反而一力承擔，就算事後被老婆判「終身監禁」，也不供出任何一位兄弟的名字。世上太少這種好兄弟，難怪這種「九叔精神」會令一眾男士們敬仰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/338337/%E8%BF%BD%E9%BE%8Dii-%E8%AD%89-%E5%AF%92%E6%88%B0-%E6%9D%8Esir%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%85-%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BC%9D-%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89%E5%94%94%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%BA%E5%97%8C%E6%88%91%E4%B9%9D%E5%8F%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F338337%2F%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E9%25BE%258Dii-%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E5%25AF%2592%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E6%259D%258Esir%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B4%2585-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BC%259D-%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25B0%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2597%258C%25E6%2588%2591%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%258F%2594&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BA0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=dfca7d39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/338337/%E8%BF%BD%E9%BE%8Dii-%E8%AD%89-%E5%AF%92%E6%88%B0-%E6%9D%8Esir%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%85-%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BC%9D-%E4%BB%B2%E6%9C%89%E5%94%94%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%BA%E5%97%8C%E6%88%91%E4%B9%9D%E5%8F%94</a>"},{"pid":"65c418eaebfacf4a362d502efc041655dcd81bfb","tid":1268228,"uid":50275,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"狗叔？<br />\n<br />\n黑社會同警察大和解？"},{"pid":"43c13afa45c41bc6432131c9d29410d8a33bba38","tid":1268228,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"兩登仔點會估到吹捧咗咁多年既九叔會咁樣反咬自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfc577fef25493499cfd76479100cadcd83e83f","tid":1268228,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"三毛仔今日想用梁家輝嚟洗版，大家睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09d075edac8163d5a8521ea60e5cb4321bad986","tid":1268228,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"美中和好未"},{"pid":"878aaba763fb823f0ea994e7624b4031aaee5429","tid":1268228,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:57:30.000Z","msg":"樓上撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇路"},{"pid":"526325d5f563695380343c7045993cecfaa7c3a4","tid":1268228,"uid":208227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"係啦 狗叔吖嘛"},{"pid":"941e6f0cd0427fd7235305a2f8f435ad98d99cb2","tid":1268228,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"878aaba763fb823f0ea994e7624b4031aaee5429","tid":1268228,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":